co-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 02, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rha1719912186511.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rha1719912186511.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rha1719912186511.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xpr1665703009007\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $nmforms\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"xpr1665703009007___nmforms_276985\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return a list of all non-modal form instances in the component pool.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"xpr1665703009007__topic_d86738e1_d86739e1_d86740e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xpr1665703009007__p_d86741e1_d86742e1_d86743e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$nmforms</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xpr1665703009007__topic_d57692e1_d57693e1_d57694e1_d57695e1_d57696e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d608030e66\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xpr1665703009007__li_d34853e1_d34854e1_d34855e1\">String containing a list of form instance names. (This list can be manipulated with ProcScript statements such as <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">getitem</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">getlistitems</span>, and so on.)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xpr1665703009007__li_d34856e1_d34857e1_d34858e1\">Empty string (\"\"), if no non-modal forms have been started.\n </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xpr1665703009007__topic_d57697e1_d57698e1_d57699e1_d57700e1_d57701e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d608030e87\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xpr1665703009007__p_d86750e1_d86751e1_d86752e1\">Use in Form components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xpr1665703009007__section_pwx_qht_xbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d608030e96\">Example: Listing Active Non-Modal Forms</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example could be used to fill the field LISTBOX with the\n            list of non-modal forms that are currently active:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"xpr1665703009007__pre_k22_sht_xbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$valrep(LISTBOX) = $nmforms</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">To allow the user to change focus to the desired form, the Detail trigger\n            for LISTBOX contains the following code:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"xpr1665703009007__pre_l22_sht_xbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger detail ; for LISTBOX\nif (LISTBOX != \" \")\n setformfocus LISTBOX\nendif\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ryt1665702577808.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>newinstance</a><p>Creates a new instance of a component.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7423308\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7423308\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$nmforms Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 02, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $nmforms Return a list of all non-modal form instances in the component pool. $nmforms Return Values String containing a list of form instance names. (This list can be manipulated with ProcScript statements such as getitem , getlistitems , and so on.) Empty string (\"\"), if no non-modal forms have been started. Use Use in Form components. Example: Listing Active Non-Modal Forms The following example could be used to fill the field LISTBOX with the list of non-modal forms that are currently active: $valrep(LISTBOX) = $nmforms Copy To allow the user to change focus to the desired form, the Detail trigger for LISTBOX contains the following code: trigger detail ; for LISTBOX if (LISTBOX != \" \") setformfocus LISTBOX endif end Copy Related Links newinstance Creates a new instance of a component. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}